          <div class="faq-answer">SEO reseller tools let agencies sell SEO to clients without doing the work in-house. Some are fulfillment services that handle content, links, and local SEO under your brand. Others are white-label platforms that give you branded dashboards and reports. You buy at wholesale. Sell at retail. Keep the margin.</div>
