        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What margins should I expect from SEO reselling?<span class="faq-icon"><svg><use href="#i-plus"/></svg></span></button>
          <div class="faq-answer">Tool-based reselling (content, reporting) delivers 80–93% margins. Managed service reselling delivers 50–67%. The difference: tools automate fulfillment. Managed services use human labor you're paying for. Automation scales. Labor doesn't.</div>
